prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card. A whimsical and humorous botanical scene. In the center, cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao (woman on left in photo) and Jordan (man on right in photo) are depicted. Lao Lao is wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt and is joyfully holding a giant, oversized leafy monstera plant in a terracotta pot, almost comically large, as if it's a birthday present. Jordan is standing slightly behind her, wearing a tan hoodie, with a playful expression, pretending to struggle under the weight of an even larger, imaginary stack of presents that are just out of frame, indicated by his straining pose.

Surrounding them is a chaotic yet charming jungle of house plants. Two small, cute, cartoon dogs (a corgi and a shiba inu) are tangled playfully in a string of party lights woven between the potted plants. One dog has a tiny party hat on its head. The background is a soft, solid pastel color.

In the center of the card, floating above the couple, is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" written in a beautiful, flowing, hand-drawn cursive script. The composition is vibrant, funny, and full of life, blending the botanical theme with a lighthearted, personal moment.
